Convolytic transforms your Vapi agents into measurable, optimizable assets. By connecting your Vapi account, you instantly unlock deep insights into agent performance, sentiment trends, and customer experience quality. No complex setup or data engineering required—just plug in your Vapi API key and start improving your AI conversations with data-backed clarity.

## Key Benefits

- **Instant Integration:**
  Connect Vapi to Convolytic using your API key. Within minutes, your agents' calls and chat transcripts are automatically analyzed and visualized in real time.

- **Voice & Chat Analytics:**
  Track performance metrics like conversion rate, sentiment, and conversation length. Identify what's working—and where your AI agents lose users.

- **A/B Testing for Prompts & Voices:**
  Run controlled experiments on agent personalities, models, and prompts to see which combinations yield higher customer satisfaction or better business outcomes.

- **Outcome Tagging & Sentiment Analysis:**
  Automatically detect positive, negative, or neutral outcomes and visualize them across time, agent, or customer type. Convolytic turns every call into actionable intelligence.

- **Integrations & Dashboards:**
  Connect to your favorite tools, export data via API, or view it all in Convolytic's sleek dashboard—designed for agencies, enterprises, and product teams running multiple AI agents.

- **White-Label Dashboard:**
  Reach out to [admin@convolytic.com](mailto:admin@convolytic.com) to enable white-label dashboard capabilities for your agency.

## How It Works

1. **Create an Agent:**
   Set up your agent in the Vapi agents dashboard.

2. **Connect Your Vapi Account:**
   Input your Vapi Agent ID and API Key in Convolytic.

3. **Data Sync:**
   Convolytic pulls real-time conversation data, including transcripts and metadata, directly from Vapi.

4. **Analytics Activation:**
   Access interactive dashboards showing sentiment trends, performance charts, and outcome analysis.

5. **Optimization:**
   Launch A/B tests, compare model or voice performance, and continuously improve your AI agents.

